      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;motivation--definition&#34;&gt;Motivation &amp;amp; Definition&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Let $X$ be a set. We would like to formalize a notion of ‘closeness’ between two points without necessarily referring to a specific &lt;a href=https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space.md class=&#34;internalLink references&#34; title=&#34;Metric Space&#34; mathLink=&#34;&#34; onmouseover=&#34;previewSide(&amp;#34;https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space.md&amp;#34;, {&amp;#34;Date&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lastmod&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;PublishDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;ExpiryDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;0001-01-01T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Aliases&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;BundleType&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Description&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Draft&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsHome&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Keywords&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;Kind&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Layout&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;LinkTitle&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;Metric Space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsNode&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsPage&amp;#34;:true,&amp;#34;Path&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;/metric_space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Slug&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lang&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsSection&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Section&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Sitemap&amp;#34;:{&amp;#34;ChangeFreq&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Priority&amp;#34;:-1,&amp;#34;Filename&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;sitemap.xml&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Disable&amp;#34;:false},&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Weight&amp;#34;:0});&#34; onmouseleave=&#34;clearPreviewSide({&amp;#34;Date&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lastmod&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;PublishDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;ExpiryDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;0001-01-01T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Aliases&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;BundleType&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Description&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Draft&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsHome&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Keywords&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;Kind&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Layout&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;LinkTitle&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;Metric Space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsNode&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsPage&amp;#34;:true,&amp;#34;Path&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;/metric_space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Slug&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lang&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsSection&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Section&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Sitemap&amp;#34;:{&amp;#34;ChangeFreq&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Priority&amp;#34;:-1,&amp;#34;Filename&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;sitemap.xml&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Disable&amp;#34;:false},&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Weight&amp;#34;:0});&#34; onclick=&#34;updateCurrentSide(event, &amp;#34;https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space.md&amp;#34;, {&amp;#34;Date&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lastmod&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;PublishDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T21:37:43-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;ExpiryDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;0001-01-01T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Aliases&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;BundleType&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Description&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Draft&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsHome&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Keywords&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;Kind&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Layout&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;LinkTitle&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;Metric Space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsNode&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsPage&amp;#34;:true,&amp;#34;Path&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;/metric_space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Slug&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lang&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsSection&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Section&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Sitemap&amp;#34;:{&amp;#34;ChangeFreq&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Priority&amp;#34;:-1,&amp;#34;Filename&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;sitemap.xml&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Disable&amp;#34;:false},&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Weight&amp;#34;:0});&#34;&gt;metric&lt;/a&gt;, but rather, via certain subsets of $X$ called &lt;em&gt;open sets&lt;/em&gt;. One can think of these open sets as specifying ‘proximity’ without necessarily satisfying the triangle inequality.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;  The following definition is motivated by some properties&lt;a href=https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space_generates_a_topology.md class=&#34;internalLink justifications ghostLink dag&#34; title=&#34;&#34; mathLink=&#34;&#34; onmouseover=&#34;previewSide(&amp;#34;https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space_generates_a_topology.md&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;nopPage&amp;#34;);&#34; onmouseleave=&#34;clearPreviewSide(&amp;#34;nopPage&amp;#34;);&#34; onclick=&#34;updateCurrentSide(event, &amp;#34;https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/metric_space_generates_a_topology.md&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;nopPage&amp;#34;);&#34;&gt;$^\dagger$&lt;/a&gt; of open sets generated by a metric $d$ on $X$, which we now axiomatize. It can also be motivated&lt;a href=https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/topological_space.md/#Open%20$%5cLeftrightarrow$%20Semi-decidable class=&#34;internalLink references dag&#34; title=&#34;Topological Space&#34; mathLink=&#34;&#34; onmouseover=&#34;previewSide(&amp;#34;https://zhaoshenzhai.github.io/mathwiki/topological_space.md/#Open $\\Leftrightarrow$ Semi-decidable&amp;#34;, {&amp;#34;Date&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lastmod&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;PublishDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;ExpiryDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;0001-01-01T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Aliases&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;BundleType&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Description&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Draft&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsHome&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Keywords&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;Kind&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Layout&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;LinkTitle&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;Topological Space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsNode&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsPage&amp;#34;:true,&amp;#34;Path&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;/topological_space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Slug&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lang&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsSection&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Section&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Sitemap&amp;#34;:{&amp;#34;ChangeFreq&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Priority&amp;#34;:-1,&amp;#34;Filename&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;sitemap.xml&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Disable&amp;#34;:false},&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Weight&amp;#34;:0});&#34; onmouseleave=&#34;clearPreviewSide({&amp;#34;Date&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lastmod&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;PublishDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2024-05-14T14:45:50-04:00&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;ExpiryDate&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;0001-01-01T00:00:00Z&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Aliases&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;BundleType&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Description&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Draft&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsHome&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Keywords&amp;#34;:null,&amp;#34;Kind&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;page&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Layout&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;LinkTitle&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;Topological Space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsNode&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;IsPage&amp;#34;:true,&amp;#34;Path&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;/topological_space&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Slug&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Lang&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;en&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;IsSection&amp;#34;:false,&amp;#34;Section&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Sitemap&amp;#34;:{&amp;#34;ChangeFreq&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;Priority&amp;#34;:-1,&amp;#34;Filename&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;sitemap.xml&am